”Gaynor Thomas
1942-2005
She walks in beauty, like the night
Of cloudless climes and starry skies;
A mind at peace with all below,
A heart whose love is innocent."╣
Č[{"URL":"/image/46a1038064ef3835444805b7368e4d9c8bdb542d","licence":"CC BY-SA 4.0","media_type":"bench","sha1":"46a1038064ef3835444805b7368e4d9c8bdb542d","width":4032,"height":3024}]"╝
╣IN LOVING MEMORY OF
KATHLEEN MILLICAN (KRIS)
1951-2021
WHO LOVED KEW GARDENS.

GONE ARE THE DAYS WE USED
TO SHARE. IN OUR HEARTS
YOU ARE ALWAYS THERE. SO
SADLY MISSED AND LOVED."┐
